Summary: Taking pictures of sky before approaching storm, did not notice these objects until pictures were looked at.
divs: sighting detailsi went into my back yard to take some pictures of an approaching storm. i was facing s\sw when i took these photos . when taking these pictures i did not notice anything in the sky, i had been looking for birds or aircraft as i did not want anything in the sky other than the clouds in the picture. had i noticed these objects in the sky i would have attached the zoom lens to the camera for a closer picture. after i had put the photo in question on the computer, thats when i noticed these objects. the one object farthest to the right appears cylindrical and the other object appears cylindrical but there seems to be some sort of winglets at either end of this object.
